---
title: Ground Lamb Navarin Stew with Creamy Mashed Potatoes
description: This French-inspired lamb stew is packed with the aromatic trifecta of onions, celery and carrots. Ground lamb and creamy mashed potatoes make it the perfect dish to satisfy your comfort food craving.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-navarin-dagneau-5781044d.jpg
